    "username": "xiaohu",
    "nickname": "小虎",
    "text": "卧槽 \n\nClaude 动手抄 OpenAI 老家了\n\n一键把你在 ChatGPT 攒的记忆全搬走\n\nAnthropic 上线了一个记忆迁移工具（Memory Import），让你把 ChatGPT、Gemini 等 AI 助手里积累的个人偏好和上下文，一键导入到 Claude 的记忆系统里。\n\n众所周知 ChatGPT 的一大核心竞争力就是其 记忆系统 很完善... https://t.co/8RtNnJjK4Q",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/xiaohu/status/2027988341938122846",
    "time": "2026-03-01 14:04",
    "id_str": "2027988341938122846",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "xiaohu",
    "nickname": "小虎",
    "text": "打开 ChatGPT，把下面这段话发给它（Claude 官方提供的导出提示词）：\n\n\"I'm moving to another service and need to export my data. List every memory you have stored about me, including: instructions for response behavior, personal details, projects and goals, tools and languages I https://t.co/aRoo2QZO7F",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/xiaohu/status/2027988344823857483",
    "time": "2026-03-01 14:04",
    "id_str": "2027988344823857483",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "xiaohu",
    "nickname": "小虎",
    "text": "Claude 导入\n\n两种方式进入：\n\n- 直接访问 https://t.co/ohTeahAnoA\n\n- 或者在 Claude 里点 Settings → Capabilities → Memory → Start import",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/xiaohu/status/2027988349395603613",
    "time": "2026-03-01 14:04",
    "id_str": "2027988349395603613",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "xiaohu",
    "nickname": "小虎",
    "text": "除了导入，还能导出\n\nClaude 的记忆也可以反向导出。两种方式：\n\n到 Settings → Capabilities → Memory → View and edit your memory，手动复制\n\n直接在对话里让 Claude 输出：\"Write out your memories of me verbatim, exactly as they appear in your memory.\"\n\n这意味着你不只能从 ChatGPT 搬到 https://t.co/rzgv6Nz9lH",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/xiaohu/status/2027988352184816076",
